    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic, well-maintained ride! This car is in great shape and has been clearly cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience that you can count on. It shows some light signs of use consistent with its history, but it remains a solid, high-quality vehicle that's ready for many more miles. This is a wonderful opportunity to own a dependable car that looks great and performs even better!",
